KOMPOT USER MANUAL: INTERFACE

The graphical interface is started by running "startx" in tty after
a successful login. Kompot utilises X11 display server managed by
the i3 windowing system.


KEYBINDS (i3):

Alt+NUM		  : Switch to NUM workspace.
Alt+Shift+NUM : Move window to workspace.
Alt+D		  : Open run menu.
Alt+R		  : Toggle resize mode. Adjust size with arrow keys.
Alt+ARROW	  : Switch window focus.


KEYBINDS (xTerm):

Alt+Enter	  : Open xTerm.
Shift+PrtSc	  : Copy text across xTerms.
Shift+Insert  : Paste text across xTerms.


KEYBINDS (elinks):

Insert		  : Scroll up.
Delete		  : Scroll down.
PgUp		  : Page up.
PgDn		  : Page down.
S			  : Bookmarks.
Esc			  : Open menu.


KEYBINDS (qutebrowser):

:			  : Begin command.
Ctrl+T		  : Open new tab.
D			  : Close tab.
U			  : Undo tab close.
Ctrl+NUM	  : Switch tabs.
Ctrl+H		  : Open homepage.
Shift+H		  : Previous page.
Shift+J		  : Next page.


KEYBINDS (irssi):

Esc+NUM		  : Open tab NUM.
